<subSubSection pageId="46" pageNumber="47" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="46.[151,1436,1518,1689]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,1590,1616]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Comments:</emphasis>
According to 
<bibRefCitation author="Barber, H. G. &amp; Sailer, R. I." box="[494,751,1590,1617]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" pagination="150 - 162" refId="ref44950" refString="Barber, H. G. &amp; Sailer, R. I. (1953) A revision of the turtle bugs of North America (Hemiptera: Pentatomidae). Journal of the Washington Academy of Sciences, 43 (5), 150 - 162." type="journal article" year="1953">Barber &amp; Sailer (1953)</bibRefCitation>
, many of the early records of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Palisot de Beauvois" baseAuthorityYear="1805" box="[1079,1324,1591,1617]" class="Insecta" family="Pentatomidae" genus="Amaurochrous" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dubius">
<emphasis box="[1079,1324,1591,1617]" italics="true" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Amaurochrous dubius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be referred to this species. 
<bibRefCitation author="Hoffman, R. L." box="[419,601,1627,1653]" pageId="46" pageNumber="47" pagination="1 - 61" refId="ref51725" refString="Hoffman, R. L. (1971) The Insects of Virginia: No. 4. Shield Bugs (Hemiptera; Scutelleroidea, Corimelaenidae, Cydnidae, Pentatomidae). Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University, Research Division Bulletin, 67, i - v + 1 - 61, 7 maps, 1 pl." type="book chapter" year="1971">Hoffman (1971)</bibRefCitation>
gave the distribution for this species as “Southeastern 
<collectingCountry box="[1217,1371,1627,1653]" name="United States of America" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">United States</collectingCountry>
, from 
<collectingRegion box="[151,260,1663,1689]" country="United States of America" name="Maryland" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Maryland</collectingRegion>
to 
<collectingRegion box="[296,413,1663,1689]" country="United States of America" name="Louisiana" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Louisiana</collectingRegion>
”; we have not found an authentic published record for 
<collectingRegion box="[1025,1138,1663,1689]" country="United States of America" name="Maryland" pageId="46" pageNumber="47">Maryland</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
